canonical:
  title: 鎭浦歸帆
  author: 李穡
  language: lzh
  text: 細雨桃花浪淸霜蘆葉秋歸帆何處落渺渺一扁舟
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 鎭浦歸帆
  author: 李穡
  language: lzh
  text: 細雨桃花浪。淸霜蘆葉秋。歸帆何處落。渺渺一扁舟。
korean:
  title: 진포 귀범
  author: 이색
  language: kor
  text: |-
    가느다란 실비에 복사꽃 물결이요
    맑은 서리에 갈대잎 가을이로구나
    돌아오는 돛대는 어느 곳에 떨어질꼬
    아득해라 조각 배 한 척
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0550&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: Returning Sail at Jinpo
  author: Lee Saek
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Fine rain weaves ripples through the peach blossoms,
    Clear frost settles on the autumn reeds.
    Where will the homeward sail finally rest?
    A solitary boat drifts on and on, lost in mist.
  footnotes:
    - Jinpo (鎭浦) is a historical Korean port, lending geographical specificity to this meditation on return and transience.
